de.upb.m2m.quality.casestudies.javaemf
Class ShapesRule2

java.lang.Object
  de.upb.m2m.quality.casestudies.javaemf.ShapesRule2

public class ShapesRule2
extends java.lang.Object

This transformation specifies a hierarchical flattening that moves every shape from inner blocks to the root block of a given shapes model. Implementation time: 15 Minutes.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Sebastian Lehrig (lehrig@mail.upb.de)
See Also:
Plugin "Rule2" (original scenario)

transform

public void transform()
Executes the transformation from a Shapes model to a new Shapes model. First copies the model, then gets the root block and iteratively moves model elements contained in subblocks to the root block. Subblocks are deleted afterwards.
